i%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ph%C3%A1p-kh%C3%BAc-hi%E1%BA%BFn-ti%C3%AAn-%C3%A2m-Th%C3%ADnh-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1t-di-%C4%91%C3%A0n-Nam-c%E1%BA%A7m/poem-qPj2I8XToUQs1F0p_mXiHA">Pháp khúc hiến tiên âm - Thính Trần Bát di đàn Nam cầm - 法曲獻仙音－聽陳八姨彈南琴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Truy-th%C3%B9-c%E1%BB%91-Cao-Th%E1%BB%A5c-ch%C3%A2u-nh%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD/poem-3sPbsnBdTJGLI6krevujEg">Truy thù cố Cao Thục châu nhân nhật kiến ký - 追酬故高蜀州人日見寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/V%E1%BB%8Dng-xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-a4-LIwzBkXIkbL9zTRP2bA">Vọng xuân từ kỳ 2 - 春望詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author-YFc6G7OeOIRiUPVl88lFdA">Tiết Đào</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-huy%E1%BB%81n-ng%E1%BB%8Dc-th%E1%BB%91-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83m-trang-nghi%C3%AAm/poem-YNITS1r9wadWAqqDb-f5mQ">Vô đề (Lương huyền ngọc thố điểm trang nghiêm) - 無題（梁懸玉兔點莊嚴）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-1olZ3UNbr3C-_4X52NnUtA">Tự Đức hoàng đế</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
